            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "This seems to fix the problem:\n```diff\ndiff --git a/src/nvim/decoration.c b/src/nvim/decoration.c\nindex f0cf24fa28..5771b3f029 100644\n--- a/src/nvim/decoration.c\n+++ b/src/nvim/decoration.c\n@@ -778,6 +778,8 @@ next_mark:\n     bool keep;\n     if (r->end_row < row || (r->end_row == row && r->end_col <= col)) {\n       keep = r->start_row >= row && decor_virt_pos(r);\n+    } else if (r->start_row > row || (r->start_row == row && r->start_col > col)) {\n+      keep = false;\n     } else {\n       keep = true;\n \n```\nBut I'm not sure if it's the correct solution.\n\ncc @vanaigr",
